9 An Act relating to the Security Breach Notification
Act; amending 24 O.S. 2021, Sections 162, 163, 164,
10 165, and 166, which relate to definitions, duty to
disclose breach, notice, enforcement, and
11 application; modifying definitions; requiring notice
of security breach of certain information; requiring
12 notice to Attorney General under certain
circumstances; specifying contents of required
13 notice; providing exemptions from certain notice
requirements; requiring confidentiality of certain
14 information submitted to Attorney General;
authorizing Attorney General to promulgate rules;
15 clarifying compliance with certain notice
requirements; modifying authorized civil penalties
16 for certain violations; providing exemptions from
certain liability; limiting liability for violations
17 under certain circumstances; modifying applicability
of act; updating statutory language; updating
18 statutory references; and providing an effective
date.
